title: Abbey and Janice: Beauty and the Best
overview: Two huge personalities, one incredible ambition, a series of set-piece challenges and a whole heap of conflict all make for an unforgettable series. Abbey Clancy is a girl with ambition. After a crack at the modelling business in the UK she's got her sights set on bigger and better things: the US. And who better to assist her than the woman who put the super into supermodel, the legendary Janice Dickinson.
